{{Infobox person |name=Laurence Coriat |birth_name= |birth_place=[[France]] |birth_date= |occupation=[[Screenwriter]], [[film director]] }} '''Laurence Coriat''' is a French screenwriter and short film director,<ref>{{cite web |url=https://movies.nytimes.com/person/422054/Laurence-Coriat |title=Laurence Coriat - About This Person - Movies & TV - NYTimes.com |publisher=Movies.nytimes.com |date= |accessdate=2013-07-23}}</ref> best known for her work with [[Michael Winterbottom]]. ==Biography== Coriat was born in France and moved to England in her twenties.<ref>http://www.patagoniamovie.com/patagoniamovie/castcrew_lc.html</ref> In 1999, she teamed with British filmmaker [[Michael Winterbottom]] on ''[[Wonderland (1999 film)|Wonderland]]''<ref>{{cite web |url=https://movies.nytimes.com/movie/review?res=9F0DE6DA163DF93BA15754C0A9669C8B63 |last=Mitchell |first=Elvis |accessdate=2013-07-23 |date=2000-07-28 |publisher=Movies.nytimes.com |title=Wonderland (1999) FILM REVIEW; Three Sisters in London, With Lives Worth Mourning}}</ref> which was selected in competition at Cannes in 1999 and won the best British Independent Film award that year. She would work with Winterbottom again on ''[[A Summer in Genoa]]'',<ref>{{cite web |url=https://movies.nytimes.com/movie/446560/Genova/details?gwh=A17CDEF31DEE0CE2CFF92554B2A257C4 |title=Genova - Cast, Crew, Director and Awards - NYTimes.com |publisher=Movies.nytimes.com |date= |accessdate=2013-07-23}}</ref>. Other features include ''[[Me Without You (film)|Me Without You]]'', ''[[Hunky Dory (film)|Hunky Dory]]'' and ''[[Patagonia (film)|Patagonia]]''.
In 2018, she wrote for the British [[crime drama]] television series ''McMafia'', inspired by the book ''McMafia: A Journey Through the Global Criminal Underworld'' (2008) by journalist [[Misha Glenny]].<ref name=goodreads>{{Cite web|url=https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/1906500.McMafia|title=McMafia|website=Goodreads|access-date=2018-02-26}}</ref> == Filmography == {| class="wikitable" |- style="background:#ccc; text-align:center;" ! Production ! Notes ! Distributor |- |''Wonderland'' | Directed by Michael Winterbottom | USA Films |- |''Me Without You'' | Directed by [[Sandra Goldbacher]] | [[Momentum Pictures]] |- |''Genova'' | Directed by Michael Winterbottom | Metrodome |- |''Patagonia'' | Directed by [[Marc Evans]] | Verve Pictures |- |''[[Hunky Dory (film)|Hunky Dory]]'' | Directed by Marc Evans | [[Entertainment One]] |- |''[[Everyday (film)|Everyday]]'' | Directed by Michael Winterbottom | [[Channel 4]] |- |''Ladygrey'' | Directed by Alain Choquart | Rézo Films |- |''[[McMafia]]'' | *Episode 1.5 (2018) *Episode 1.6 (2018) |[[BBC One]] |}
